title: Taco spice mix (paprika free)
ingredients: ['4 tablespoons dried minced onion', '4 teaspoons cornflour', '1 tablespoon dried oregano', '2 small beef stock cubes', '1 tablespoon ground cumin', '4 tablespoons chilli powder', '1 tablespoon garlic powder', '1 tablespoon onion powder', '1 teaspoon Cayenne pepper']
